{"tid":621201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"調查：四成考生認為家長在文憑試中有給予壓力","createTime":"2018-04-08T06:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T23:52:26.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"06bfa400f2acb820c76257c236058357d136d258","tid":621201,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"學友社進行調查，了解應屆文憑試考生的應試壓力，結果顯示四成考生認為家長在文憑試中有給予壓力。<br />\n<br />\n學友社學生輔導中心總幹事吳寶城說，部分家長過分關心子女，會令考生感到煩擾，造成壓力。<br />\n<br />\n有應屆文憑試考生家長相信，兒子的壓力是源於對自己的要求。她又說，學校估計考生文憑試成績，亦會對他們構成壓力。<br />\n<br />\n中心副總幹事陳倩雯建議，家長應多了解子女的身心狀況及考試時間表，有助掌握子女在不同階段的需要，亦能減低家長本身的壓力。她又希望家長能在子女的考試路上，擔任同行者角色，讓子女感受到支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90%E8%80%83%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%9C%A8%E6%96%87%E6%86%91%E8%A9%A6%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E7%B5%A6%E4%BA%88%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B-045514806.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%2580%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2586%2591%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E4%25BA%2588%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%258A%259B-045514806.html&d=IHyLF%2BKTKc3wSGV5mAMi0ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ad61c28f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90%E8%80%83%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%9C%A8%E6%96%87%E6%86%91%E8%A9%A6%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E7%B5%A6%E4%BA%88%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B-045514806.html</a>"},{"pid":"b5bc98c4dd1af1fa74629761a4675ff354bcfab8","tid":621201,"uid":61864,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:28:24.000Z","msg":"真係得四成咁少？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941e86809d10d46bb728f157063fd7a56e53b244","tid":621201,"uid":35070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:30:39.00